Properties.commandText:
SELECT TOP(2) [u].[Id], [u].[AccessFailedCount], [u].[CreatedOn], [u].[Email], [u].[EmailConfirmed], [u].[FirstName], [u].[IsDeleted], [u].[LastName], [u].[LockoutEnabled], [u].[LockoutEnd], [u].[PasswordHashed], [u].[PhoneNumber], [u].[PhoneNumberConfirmed]
FROM [Users] AS [u]
WHERE LOWER([u].[Email]) = @__ToLower_0
ORDER BY [u].[Id]

SELECT [s].[UserId], [s].[RoleId], [s].[AssignedOn], [s].[Id], [s].[Name], [u1].[Id]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [u].[Id]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    WHERE LOWER([u].[Email]) = @__ToLower_0
) AS [u1]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [u0].[UserId], [u0].[RoleId], [u0].[AssignedOn], [r].[Id], [r].[Name]
    FROM [UserRoles] AS [u0]
    INNER JOIN [Roles] AS [r] ON [u0].[RoleId] = [r].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [u1].[Id] = [s].[UserId]
ORDER BY [u1].[Id]
